<inglise> Payment to the party concerned shall be effected in accordance with the choice indicated in the latter's proposal: </inglise>
<eesti> Tasumine asjaomasele poolele toimub asjaomase isiku ettepanekus m&auml;rgitud viisil: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) within six weeks of the date of signature of the contract, a single payment on account amounting to 60 % of the Community contribution; or </inglise>
<eesti> a) kuue kuu jooksul p&auml;rast lepingu allkirjastamist &uuml;he osamaksena, mis v&otilde;ib moodustada &uuml;hendusepoolsest rahastamisest kuni 60%, v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise> (b) at two-monthly intervals, four equal instalments each amounting to 20 % of the Community contribution, the first such instalment being paid within six weeks of the date of signature of the contract. </inglise>
<eesti> b) kahekuuliste vahedega nelja v&otilde;rdse osamaksena, millest iga makse v&otilde;ib moodustada &uuml;hendusepoolsest rahastamisest kuni 20% ja mille esimene osamakse tasutakse kuue kuu jooksul alates lepingu allkirjastamiskuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise> However, while a contract is being executed, the competent authority may: </inglise>
<eesti> Lepingu t&auml;itmisel v&otilde;ib p&auml;dev asutus: </eesti>
<inglise> - defer payment of an instalment either wholly or in part where it finds, in particular during the checks referred to in Article 6 (2), irregularities in carrying out the measures concerned or a substantial interval between the due date for payment of the instalment and the date when the party concerned actually incurs the forecast expenditure; </inglise>
<eesti> - l&uuml;kata osamakse tasumise kas t&auml;ielikult v&otilde;i osaliselt edasi, kui ta avastab eriti artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 2 osutatud kontrollide k&auml;igus asjaomaste meetmete rakendamises eeskirjade eiramise v&otilde;i olulise vahe osamakse tasumise kuup&auml;eva ja kuup&auml;eva vahel, mil asjaomasel isikul tekib eeldatav kulu; </eesti>
<inglise> - in exceptional cases, pay in advance an instalment either wholly or in part if the party concerned submits a reasoned application showing that he must incur a substantial part of the expenditure significantly earlier than the date laid down for payment of the Community contribution. </inglise>
<eesti> - maksta erandjuhtudel osamakse t&auml;ielikult v&otilde;i osaliselt ette, kui asjaomane isik esitab p&otilde;hjendatud taotluse, milles on n&auml;idatud, et oluline osa tema kuludest tekib &uuml;hendusepoolse toetuse maksmiseks s&auml;testatud kuup&auml;evast m&auml;rgatavalt varem. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The payment of each instalment shall be conditional upon the lodging with the competent authority of a security equal to the amount of the instalment, plus 10 %. </inglise>
<eesti> Osamaksete tasumiseks tuleb p&auml;devale asutusele esitada osamakse summaga v&otilde;rdne tagatis, millele on lisatud 10%. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Securities shall be released and the balance shall be paid subject to: </inglise>
<eesti> Tagatiste vabastamise ja j&auml;relej&auml;&auml;nud osa maksmise tingimuseks on: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the forwarding to the Commission and to the competent authority of the report referred to in Article 8 (1) and to verification of the details contained in that report; </inglise>
<eesti> a) artikli 8 l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud aruande edastamine komisjonile ja p&auml;devale asutusele ning k&otilde;nealuse aruande &uuml;ksikasjade kontrollimine; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) confirmation by the competent authority that the party concerned has fulfilled his obligations as laid down in the contract; and </inglise>
<eesti> b) p&auml;deva asutuse kinnitus, et asjaomane isik on t&auml;itnud oma lepingus s&auml;testatud kohustused ja </eesti>
<inglise> (c) confirmation by the competent authority that the party concerned or any third party named in the contract has spent his own contribution for the purposes laid down. </inglise>
<eesti> c) p&auml;deva asutuse kinnitus, et asjaomane isik v&otilde;i lepingus nimetatud mis tahes kolmas isik on tasunud s&auml;testatud eesm&auml;rgi puhul oma osa. </eesti>
<inglise> However, at the reasoned request of the party concerned, the balance may be paid after the measure has been executed and the report referred to in Article 8 has been forwarded, provided that securities have been lodged which cover the total amount of the Community contribution plus 10 %. </inglise>
<eesti> Asjaomase isiku p&otilde;hjendatud taotluse korral v&otilde;ib j&auml;relej&auml;&auml;nud summa maksta p&auml;rast meetme t&auml;ideviimist ja artiklis 8 osutatud aruande edastamist, tingimusel et asjaomane isik on esitatud tagatise, mis katab kogu &uuml;hendusepoolse toetuse summa, millele on lisatud 10%. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> In so far as the conditions set out in paragraph 3 are not fulfilled, securities shall be forfeit. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatud tingimusi ei t&auml;ideta, j&auml;&auml;dakse tagatisest ilma. </eesti>
<inglise> In that event, the amount in question shall be deducted from the European Agricultural Guidance and Guarantee Fund (EAGGF), Guarantee Section, expenditure and more particularly from that arising out of the measures referred to in Article 4 of Regulation (EEC) No 1079/77. </inglise>
<eesti> Sel juhul arvatakse k&otilde;nealune summa maha Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi (EAGGF) tagatisrahastu kuludest ja eriti m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1079/77 artiklis 4 osutatud meetmetest tulenevatest kuludest. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 8 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 8 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Each party responsible for one of the measures referred to in this Regulation shall submit to the competent authority, within four months of the final date fixed in the contract for execution of the measures, a detailed report on the utilization of the Community funds allocated and on the foreseeable results of the measures in question. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;ik pooled, kes vastutavad m&otilde;ne k&auml;eolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses osutatud meetme eest, esitavad p&auml;devale asutusele nelja kuu jooksul alates meetmete t&auml;ideviimist k&auml;sitlevas lepingus kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud l&otilde;ppkuup&auml;evast &uuml;ksikasjaliku aruande &uuml;henduse eraldatud summade kasutamise ja k&otilde;nealuse meetme kavandatavate tulemuste kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> If that report is submitted later than four months after that final date, 10 % of the Community contribution shall be withheld for each month commenced after expiry of that time limit. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui k&otilde;nealune aruanne esitatakse hiljem kui neli kuud p&auml;rast k&otilde;nealust l&otilde;ppkuup&auml;eva, peetakse iga p&auml;rast k&otilde;nealuse t&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppu alanud kuu puhul kinni 10% &uuml;henduse toetusest. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The competent authority concerned shall forward to the Commission a statement to the effect that each contract has been performed satisfactorily together with a copy of the final report. </inglise>
<eesti> Asjaomane p&auml;dev asutus edastab komisjonile kinnituse lepingute rahuldava t&auml;itmise kohta ning l&otilde;pparuande koopia. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
